      <title>随着中国债券交易加速，亚洲美元债券交易量有望增长 20%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/asia-dollar-bond-volumes-seen-rising-20-china-deals-gather-pace-2025-01-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国债务交易的推动，以及美国降息使企业发行美元债券而非本币债券的成本更低，预计2025年亚洲美元债券发行量将较去年增长20%左右。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/asia-dollar-bond-volumes-seen-rising-20-china-deals-gather-pace-2025-01-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 04:57:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国扩大消费者以旧换新计划以重振经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expands-scope-consumer-trade-ins-home-appliances-2025-01-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了重振低迷的家电市场需求，中国今年将更多家电产品纳入以旧换新范围，并将对更多数码产品提供补贴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-expands-scope-consumer-trade-ins-home-appliances-2025-01-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 03:12:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《澳大利亚人报》报道，澳大利亚联邦银行未能就现金使用费向监管机构通报</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/australias-cba-fails-notify-regulators-over-cash-access-fee-australian-reports-2025-01-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《澳大利亚人报》报道，澳大利亚联邦银行在将一百万客户转移到新的银行账户之前未能正式通知该国的任何一家审慎监管机构，导致许多人必须付费才能通过分行获取现金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/australias-cba-fails-notify-regulators-over-cash-access-fee-australian-reports-2025-01-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 01:00:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国向爱沙尼亚转移 5000 万美元没收资产，以协助起诉丹麦银行</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-transfers-50-mln-forfeited-assets-estonia-help-danske-bank-prosecution-2025-01-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部周二表示，将与爱沙尼亚分享 5000 万美元的没收资产，以表彰爱沙尼亚在成功起诉丹麦银行及相关没收行动中提供的帮助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-transfers-50-mln-forfeited-assets-estonia-help-danske-bank-prosecution-2025-01-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 20:05:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙Novo Banco解雇首席风险官，并将此事提交监管机构</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/portugals-novo-banco-fires-chief-risk-officer-refers-matter-regulator-2025-01-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Novo Banco 已解雇其首席风险官，并向葡萄牙银行业监管机构报告了对其行为的担忧，并向检察官办公室提起了诉讼，检察官办公室已展开调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/portugals-novo-banco-fires-chief-risk-officer-refers-matter-regulator-2025-01-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 14:00:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
