      <title>阿尔伯克基称欧盟金融服务市场分化相当于关税</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/eu-financial-services-markets-fragmentation-works-tariff-albuquerque-says-2025-01-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟金融服务委员玛丽亚·路易斯·阿尔伯克基周二表示，由于欧盟金融服务市场分散，欧盟金融业面临相当于 110% 关税的负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/eu-financial-services-markets-fragmentation-works-tariff-albuquerque-says-2025-01-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 13:18:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
